text: George Webster (31 July 1885 - 18 January 1941) was a British swimmer. He competed at the 1912 Summer Olympics and the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1885 births Category:1941 deaths Category:British male swimmers Category:Male backstroke swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Great Britain Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Swimmers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Halifax, West Yorkshire
